reviewText:
See images for list of artists and songs included

You've heard the Ultimate Series...Now, see the Ultimate in Rock Videos. Six incredible rock videos, together as one. Rock it out with the Who's Who of Christian Rock. Pop this video in the VCR, and jam with Degarmo & Key, Petra, REZ, White Heart, and well the list goes on.

Six Different Styles...One boldly proclaimed message to the world. the vibe's....happenin', the sound's...hard edged, the message...it's in your face!!!
